Women Safety Alert App is an open-source web application designed to enhance women's safety through emergency SOS alerts, live location sharing, trusted contacts, and nearby emergency services. Built as part of the Open Source Hackathon by Elite Coders.
A web-based Women Safety Alert System designed to enhance personal safety through technology. The platform provides quick access to emergency assistance and safety features during critical situations.

Features 
🚨 One-click SOS Alert 
📍 Live GPS Location Tracking
📞 Emergency Contact Notifications
🎤 Voice-Activated SOS ("Help Me")
🏥 Nearby Hospitals Finder 
🚔 Nearby Police Station Locator
🛣 Safe Route Finder
🤖 AI Safety Chatbot
🔐 User Login & Registration

Technologies Used HTML CSS JavaScript Objective

The goal of this project is to empower women with a reliable digital safety solution that can provide immediate assistance and help during emergencies.

